    {
      "role": "user",
      "content": "calling it a \"politically motivated talking point\" seems a bit dismissive of the actual math for these business owners. it's not just politics when they have to pay for new filtration systems or waste management right now. aren't you worried that by framing it this way, you're basically saying the survival of local manufacturing is less important than these theoretical future benefits?",
